{"tid":1960492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有望抗武肺藥物Avigan　日本擬免費提供！已30國請求提供","createTime":"2020-04-06T07:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T17:21:06.000Z","uid":75656,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"81dbc174d0eeb5cd795c1e989f787fd4dc824457","tid":1960492,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"富士軟片控股公司子公司開發的抗流感藥物法匹拉韋（Favipiravir，商品名：Avigan），被看好可治療武漢肺炎，中國宣稱有療效，日本則在進行臨床研究。日本今天表示，考慮將藥物免費提供給有需要的國家，目前已約有30國提出需求。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《共同社》報導，日本官房長官菅義偉今天表示，考慮向需要的國家免費提供Avigan，目前有約30個國家通過外交管道請求提供，之後將進行磋商並擴大臨床研究。<br />\n<br />\n中國日前宣布，利用法匹拉韋對武漢肺炎確診者進行治療的臨床研究已完成，結果顯示法匹拉韋對肺炎等症狀具療效，考慮正式採用法匹拉韋列當成武漢肺炎治療藥物之一。<br />\n<br />\n日本則從3月開始由愛知縣的藤田醫科大學附屬醫院等進行臨床研究，臨床研究的對象是80名感染病毒的輕症或無症狀者，對這些患者施予藥物後，比較病毒的數量是否減少。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/column/article/906/rnews/20200403/1727528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F906%2Frnews%2F20200403%2F1727528&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=e2b8f933\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F906%2Frnews%2F20200403%2F1727528&h=5cfd18f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/column/article/906/rnews/20200403/1727528</a><br />\n<br />\n日本路透社:<a href=\"https://jp.reuters.com/article/suga-avigan-idJPKBN21L12T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjp.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fsuga-avigan-idJPKBN21L12T&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=3c794eb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjp.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fsuga-avigan-idJPKBN21L12T&h=9957f283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jp.reuters.com/article/suga-avigan-idJPKBN21L12T</a>"},{"pid":"5ab715732865ece72313f35d71d6363b7a33f122","tid":1960492,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"81dbc174d0eeb5cd795c1e989f787fd4dc824457","tid":1960492,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,